ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: PLSC 625 is an excellent class on the theory of violence and its purposes in political progress. I would definitely recommend this class t a peer if they are interested in delving deep into the core of classical political theory.

comments: Got me thinking about questions that I'm definitely planningto continue pursuing in my future research
